<h2 class="bold font-l">Natsuki crying</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Shaken by the death of her grandmother, Natsuki stares into space before eventually breaking down </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/HeroicBSOD" class='trope-example-link'>Heroic BSoD</a></p>
